---
title: Saucy Jerk Chicken & Coconut Rice  with Sautéed Cabbage & Scallions
description: Our spin on jerk chicken—a traditional recipe from Jamaica—comes together in just 30 minutes. You’ll simmer seared chicken cutlets in jerk sauce that’s packed with tangy tamarind, garlic, chili peppers, and a pinch of brown sugar, then serve over coconut rice with a side of sautéed red cabbage and squeeze of fresh lime juice.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/67045d0299e8e2a18bd76225-31c36e75.jpeg
